    W3Schools. (2025) JavaScript setTimeout() Method. Available at: https://www.w3schools.com/jsref/met_win_settimeout.asp [Accessed 21 Augustus 2025].
    W3Schools. (2025) JavaScript DOM innerHTML. Available at: https://www.w3schools.com/jsref/prop_innerhtml.asp [Accessed 21 Augustus 2025].
    Microsoft Docs. (2025) Razor Syntax: Integrate server data in JS. Available at: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/mvc/views/razor [Accessed 21 Augustus 2025].
